data.text:
Introducing Your Health Space

The past few years have been a challenging time for those working in health care settings. The Canadian Mental Health Association (CMHA) Ontario has launched Your Health Space, a free workplace mental health service for Ontario’s health care organizations.

Text Connect to 247247

ConnexOntario now offers a text line as a fast and convenient way to reach out for mental health and addiction service information. Ontarians can text CONNEX to 247247 to connect with a system navigation specialist, 24 hours a day, seven days a week.

2021-2022 Annual Report

We’re pleased to share our 2021-2022 annual report. During COVID-19, our services remained a key priority at our branch.

Addiction Services

Are you concerned about your substance use and/or gambling or someone else’s substance use and/or gambling? We can help!
